27.06	Devdas_(2002_film)	Devdas (2002 film)	Devdas (Hindi: ) is a 2002 Bollywood film based on the 1917 Sharat Chandra Chattopadhyay novella Devdas. This is the third Hindi version and the first colour film version of the story in Hindi. The film is directed by Sanjay Leela Bhansali and stars Shahrukh Khan, Madhuri Dixit, and Aishwarya Rai in the leading roles.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/6/6d/Devdas.jpg/220px-Devdas.jpg
